thread.title: Treasury to Sell $158 Billion in Debt

author: wsjcom
title: Treasury to Sell $158 Billion in Debt
text:
The U.S. Treasury Department will auction $158 billion in securities next week, comprising $28 billion in new debt and $130 billion in previously sold debt. Details (all with minimum denominations of $100):
Monday: $51 billion in 13-week bills, a reopening of an issue first sold on Dec. 14, 2017, maturing June 14, 2018. Cusip number: 912796PL7.
